snippet.title: Konrad the Kitten - Update 2.0
snippet.description:
Konrad the Kitten is one of the cutest things you can experience in VR. Have your own virtual cat that needs your help and all your love.

Update 2.0 changes the game by not only enhancing lots of existing things but also adding a whole new world and a really exciting new major feature. 

For more information, visit http://www.KonradTheKitten.com
